text: The Premier of New Brunswick (French (masculine): Premier ministre du Nouveau- Brunswick, or feminine: Premi√®re ministre du Nouveau-Brunswick) is the first minister for the Canadian province of New Brunswick. They are the province's head of government and de facto chief executive. The current Premier of New Brunswick is Blaine Higgs, who was sworn in November 9, 2018. ==References== *
